 trình đồng chí - 城中有感寄呈同志</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Ng%C3%B4n/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-y%E1%BA%BFn-L%C3%A2m-T%C3%A2n-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Minh-Ph%E1%BB%A7-tr%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-xHNBxRg0tBwZYJtZGG5WUQ">Thu dạ yến Lâm Tân Trịnh Minh Phủ trạch - 秋夜宴臨津鄭明府宅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Ng%C3%B4n/author-m8VtavBW4Ya78m3-y_Q_Gw">Đỗ Thẩm Ngôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kim-Gyo-gak/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-t%E1%BB%AD-h%E1%BA%A1-s%C6%A1n/poem-rXhmZVwa2SRMIdBWZOJ5WA">Tống đồng tử hạ sơn - 送童子下山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kim-Gyo-gak/author-31OhGSILhV8buJqBKE9ctg">Kim Gyo-gak</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-N%C3%A3o-H%C3%A1c-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-huynh/poem-u159qYrMs2x5zxJ5w9coLw">Xuân nhật hí đề Não Hác sứ quân huynh - 春日戲題惱郝使君兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
